Ranger Help for: poison arrow
==============================

SYNTAX:      poison arrow
             poison bolt
             taint arrow
             taint bolt
USAGE:       Specific terrains
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     10
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to coat an arrow or bolt with poison, adding
toxic damage to the next shot. The Ranger needs ammo and a vial of
poison in their inventory. The 'taint' command is an alias for poison
arrow/bolt.
